Feature: User can add payment methods
        As a User
        I want to have a profile page
        So that I can add payment method

Scenario: Add payment method
Given I am a registered user
And I am on the home page
And I follow "Profile page"
And I click on "Payment methods" button
Then I should be on the "Payement Methods page"
And I click on "Add payment method" button
And I fill in "card number" with "123456789"
Then I press on "save"
And I should be on the "Profile page".

